➜realme 真我 Q2 Pro 图赏：谁说千元机不能拥有 65W 快充和素皮？
https://www.ifanr.com/1371437?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	21752
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371482" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/gg.png" alt="" width="1615" height="908" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/gg.png 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/gg-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/gg-768x432.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/gg-1024x576.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>那些用了就回不去的手机功能中，除了高刷新率，还有快充。当你的手机充电时间从 2 小时缩短至 1 小时内，你会感到舒爽，以及痛快。</p>
<p>不过随着技术的成熟，这些「旦用难回」的体验已不是旗舰机的专属。在千元机阵容中，高刷屏和快充的身影越来越多。</p>
<p>2019 年 9 月，realme 推出了 Q 系列新机，998 元的起售价率先将 20W 快充拉到了千元档。时隔一年，realme 在昨日又将 65W 闪充拉到了千元档，推出了真我 Q2i、真我 Q2 和真我 Q2 Pro。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371440" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/007dP9zpgy1gjnitotei5j335s16ox6r.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="384" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/007dP9zpgy1gjnitotei5j335s16ox6r.jpg 1024w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/007dP9zpgy1gjnitotei5j335s16ox6r-360x135.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/007dP9zpgy1gjnitotei5j335s16ox6r-768x288.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p>其中起售价为 1799 元的真我 Q2 Pro，搭载了 65W 闪充，成为当前最具性价比的快充手机之一。</p>
<p>真我 Q2 Pro 的包装盒，依然是是熟悉的橘黄色，让人一眼就能看出来自 realme 家族。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371466" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000003.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000003.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000003-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000003-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000003-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>实际上，在拿到手机前，我们还收到了 realme 的发布会「邀请函」。这个「邀请函」很有意思，外壳上印着「王炸出击，真香回归」，盒内是一副超级大的扑克牌。或许是有意为之，「大王」被放在了最上方，与其包装上的「王炸」相呼应。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371467" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000014.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000014.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000014-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000014-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000014-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>realme 的产品给我的印象，一直以来就是非常年轻，realme Q2 Pro 的设计也同样如此。其「轻潮灰」配色的后壳，使用了以往高端机上才出现的素皮材料（Vegan Leather）。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371465" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000001.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000001.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000001-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000001-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000001-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>这种材料看上去很有质感，摸起来有点像偏软的聚碳酸酯，个人比较喜欢。其右侧印着「DEAR TO LEAP」，应该是机压工艺，形成了凹凸的纹理。这句话翻译过来，其实就是 realme 品牌的 Slogan「敢越级」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371468" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000009.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000009.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000009-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000009-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000009-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>左下方是小字号的 realme 标识，是亮银色金属材质，为后盖起到了点缀的装饰作用。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371469" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000006.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000006.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000006-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000006-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000006-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>值得一提的是，机身重量只有 175 克，算是 5G 手机里比较轻的。不过素皮版的机身稍厚，来到了 8.6mm，采用 AG 玻璃工艺的「C 位色」版，厚度只有 8.1mm。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371470" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000012.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000012.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000012-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000012-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000012-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>后置摄像头共有四颗，分别是 4800 万主摄、119°超广角镜头、4cm 超级微距镜头，以及一颗黑白人像镜头。前置搭载了 1600 万像素镜头，支持超级夜景自拍。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371471" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000007.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000007.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000007-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000007-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000007-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>手机的正面是一块 6.43 英寸 Super AMOLED 显示屏，分辨率为 2400 × 1080，屏幕由三星提供，色彩、细腻度都处于上乘水准。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371472" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000010.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000010.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000010-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000010-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000010-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>对于喜欢在夜间玩手机的朋友来说，有些手机屏幕亮度即便调到最低，也会感觉过亮。realme Q2 Pro 的屏幕自动背光最低 4nit，手动最低亮度 2nit，黑暗环境下不会刺眼。并支持类 DC 调光功能，低亮度防频闪，对眼睛比较友好。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371473" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000013.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000013.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000013-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000013-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000013-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>真我 Q2 Pro 的屏占比为 90.8%，边框不算宽，但是下巴有点「厚」，千元机的属性在这一点上「暴露无疑」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371474" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000002.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000002.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000002-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000002-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000002-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>真我 Q2 Pro 的指纹识别功能没有集成在开关按键上，而是使用了光感屏下指纹，实际使用中解锁速度还是比较快的，几乎没有延迟。</p>
<p>芯片方面，真我 Q2 Pro 采用了天玑 800U，这是联发科新款 7nm 制程的 5G 芯片。对比天玑 720，其 CPU 性能提升 20%；GPU 性能提升了 28%，理论上 App 应用启动时间可加快 1.4 倍。在日常游戏体验上，如《王者荣耀》和《QQ 飞车》，可保持 60 帧稳定输出。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371475" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000005.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000005.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000005-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000005-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000005-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>值得一提的是，真我 Q2 Pro 支持双卡双待，国内三大运营商的 5G 网络均可兼容，支持双 5G 同时在线。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371477" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000017.jpg" alt="" width="1355" height="906" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000017.jpg 1355w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000017-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000017-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000017-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1355px) 100vw, 1355px" /></p>
<p>当然，真我 Q2 Pro 最香的功能还属 65W 闪充。官方表示「充电 3 分钟，就能微信文字聊天 80 分钟」。4300mAh 的电池容量，也足够支撑出门一天的续航。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371478" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000015.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000015.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000015-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000015-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000015-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>价格上，真我 Q2 Pro 8+128GB 版本为 1799 元，8+256GB 版为 1999 元。这应该是目前价格最低的 65W 快充手机了，5G 双卡双待的加持，相信能在这个价位段成为有力的竞争者。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371479" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000016.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000016.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000016-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000016-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000016-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
<p>另外两款同时发布的机型中，真我 Q2i 的价格与上一代持平，均为 998 元起步，支持 30W 快充以及 120Hz 刷新率的真我 Q2，其售价为 1299 元。</p>
<p>经过两代机型的铺垫，realme Q 系列俨然成为了「性价比」机型的代表之一。这对于学生党，以及其他预算不那么充足的朋友来说，确实非常友好。不必花数千元，就能体验到高端机型拥有的特性，享受到科技带来的美好，这或许就是真我 Q 系列最大的意义。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371480" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000008.jpg" alt="" width="1615" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000008.jpg 1615w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000008-360x241.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000008-768x514.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/000008-1024x685.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1615px) 100vw, 1615px" /></p>
